text: Ruth Hunkeler (born 18 January 1940) is a Swiss equestrian. She competed in two events at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1940 births Category:Living people Category:Swiss female equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Switzerland Category:Equestrians at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
